_sText:
My 2nd publicly submitted map! Supports maximum 66 players & includes custom bot navigation meshes.

A medium-sized Gun Game map. Features above and below ground action, as well as scalable towers for bold players seeking to maximize sight whilst risking personal safety. There's also a few out-of-the-way camping spots for those who've reached the game-winning knife kill phase looking to ambush.

This map comes in two versions:
gg_pwnpit
&
gg_pwnpit_cheap

gg_pwnpit features more scenery and enhanced bot support, but has a larger file size (~21mb total)
gg_pwnpit_cheap has a large chunk of scenery cut out and slightly less bot support, but has a smaller file size (~13mb total)
I decided to do this because I understand many Gun Game maps feature smaller file sizes as to reduce download time as much as possible. The cheap version is for server hosts who especially value download times.

I also left the upper balconies accessible via jetpack or low gravity, just for fun. It probably breaks the flow of the map, but who cares lol. I don't think there's a way to get to it beyond these two methods, so vanilla gameplay enjoyers need not worry.
